&lt;p&gt;Due to a recent retirement, a 15 hour/week vacancy has arisen for a Band 7 Macmillan Breast Clinical Nurse Specialist at the breast unit at Worthing Hospital. This position will involve working in all aspects of breast cancer care including breast screening, symptomatic services and oncology. Experience at Band 6 or above in a related field is essential as is the ability to work flexibly and cross-site. This is an ideal opportunity to join a well established team of experienced breast cancer professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
